body:
This repo is open for any sort of file storage or exchange by members of the **NYC SuperCollider group**. To gain write access to this REPO or the WIKI, please email your GitHub loginname to tintinnabuli@oneti.info .

If you wish to experiment with GitHub, per se, please run your experiments under the 'test' directory. The wiki lives at https://github.com/tintinnabuli/nysc/wiki . Feel free to create or edit pages, issues or whatever you like.

Make some noise!
